<varlistentry id="options.Font">
<term>Font <emphasis remap='I'>font</emphasis></term>
      <listitem>
<para>Specifies the font associated with this style. 
<emphasis remap='I'>font</emphasis> copuld beeither a standard X11 font definition, or a filename of the TrueType font that could be found in FontPath.
To specify the size of the TrueType font - use format like that : FontName.ttf-Size. </para>
		<example>
		<literallayout>
	Font  DefaultSans.ttf-14</literallayout>		
		</example>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
